assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: KENKO Mayonnaise Co.,Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of salads and delicatessen; mayonnaise, dressings, and sauces; and egg products in Japan. It develops salads that are used at restaurants, bakeries, and convenience stores under the Fashion Delica Foods brand name. The company also offers various processed egg products, including egg salad for use in sandwiches and delicatessen bread, rolled omelet for lunch boxes, narrowly stripped cooked eggs for use in cold Chinese noodles, and boiled eggs for oden soup. In addition, it operates Salad Café, a retail shop of fresh salad; and website store, as well as provides fresh delicatessen for supermarkets. The company was incorporated in 1958 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
